OL,3,CMasterchef winner Gareth Baty returns
OL,4,Cto his former Carlisle school
OL,6,FFormer pupil and top chef Gareth Baty
OL,7,Fhas returned to his old school.
OL,9,FAustin Friars in Carlisle is where he
OL,10,Flearnt some of his early culinary
OL,11,Fskills, before going on to become an
OL,12,Findustry leader.
OL,14,FThe Masterchef: The Professionals
OL,15,Fwinner officially opened the
OL,16,Findependent school's new Food
OL,17,FTechnology Department, which came at
OL,18,Fcost of #70,000.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/6
