OL,3,CMasterchef winner Gareth Baty returns
OL,4,Cto his former Carlisle school
OL,6,FIt will also be available to local
OL,7,Fcommunity groups and pupils from other
OL,8,Fschools to use.
OL,10,FGareth told ITV Border: "It's an
OL,11,Fhonour to be asked back. Albeit, (I
OL,12,Fwas) a little bit nervous driving back
OL,13,Fup the driveway after all these years.
OL,15,F"Getting the foundations early,
OL,16,Funderstanding the processes and just
OL,17,Fgetting some core recipes in your
OL,18,Frepertoire will carry you through the
OL,19,Frest of your life.
OL,26,@sD@bpmtD@Dpn
