OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F322A1782841688
OL,3,CMasterchef winner Gareth Baty returns
OL,4,Cto his former Carlisle school
OL,6,F"Once you understand a few basic
OL,7,Fprinciples, you can then start
OL,8,Fexperimenting and developing those
OL,9,Fskills."
OL,11,FPupils have already been busy in the
OL,12,Fnew facility, cooking vegetable
OL,13,Ffritters and learning skills from
OL,14,FGareth.
OL,16,FYear 8 Student Liberty Bull said: "I
OL,17,Fthink it'll be quite exciting in the
OL,18,Ffuture because I definitely want to
OL,19,Fchoose it as an option for GCSEs."
