OL,3,CMasterchef winner Gareth Baty returns
OL,4,Cto his former Carlisle school
OL,6,FIn the same year group, Daisy
OL,7,FBeresford said: "I think it's going to
OL,8,Fbe a good opportunity for younger and
OL,9,Folder years."
OL,11,FThe school says the food tech
OL,12,Fdepartment is is part of wider
OL,13,Finvestment.
OL,15,FHeadteacher Chris Hattam said: "We've
OL,16,Floved cooking, and the children have
OL,17,Fbeen engaged in food technology, but
OL,18,Fthey certainly haven't had facilities
OL,19,Flike this today (before).
