OL,3,CMasterchef winner Gareth Baty returns
OL,4,Cto his former Carlisle school
OL,6,F"It's been an air fryer or a couple of
OL,7,Fbaking trays in an oven.
OL,9,F"Not only are they open to the public
OL,10,Fif they want to come in and rent, but
OL,11,Fwe're actually reaching out to all the
OL,12,Flocal primary schools to offer them
OL,13,Ffree use of our food technology."
OL,15,FIt's hoped the new facility will help
OL,16,Fpupils wishing to enter the
OL,17,Fhospitality industry.
